data.description: Location, location, location... Welcome to this very sought after neighborhood in Caughlin Ranch of CastleRidge. Close to all of the shopping and amenities but also far enough away from the hustle and bustle to give you a felling a privacy.  The home nestled in a small cul-de-sac has almost all of your living space on the main floor. The only living space on the upstairs portion is a large bedroom and full bathroom (great in-law or adult student space) The home is very open and light with a large kitchen and family room area.  The back yard so meticulously maintained is truly park like.  There was a large KOI pond that has been emptied so the owner could make new homes for the KOI before the sale of the home. Owner will not make repairs.
